title: Lord of the Rings and The Hobbit Complete Discography
description:
All the Music from The Lord of the Rings and The Hobbit - An Unexpected Journey
===============================================================================

The files are encoded on Lame Encoder in 320Kbps or VBR set to high quality.

Contents
========

Original Soundtrack
-------------------

1 - The Fellowship of the Ring
2 - The Two Towers
3 - The Return of the King

The Complete Recordings
-----------------------

01 - The Fellowship of the Ring  (The Complete Recordings) (3 CDs + Score)
02 - The Two Towers (The Complete Recordings) (3 CDs + Score)
03 - The Return of the King (The Complete Recordings) (4 CDs + Score)
